kaspa-prov verify --model-id 0xabc... --release-txid 0xdef...
# checks chain inclusion, sigs, and hashes of fetched artifacts



) APIs you’d expose (indexer)

GET /models/{model_id} → summary + latest release

GET /models/{model_id}/lineage → parents/children graph

GET /events?model_id=...&type=TRAIN_STEP → paginated steps

POST /verify → submit local hashes, get pass/fail + proof

) Success metrics (MVP)

TTV (time-to-verity): < 2s after event mined (pre-finality), sealed after ~1h.

Overhead: SDK adds ≤ 1–2% wall-clock to training (uploads + commit).

Repro score: Independent verifier can reproduce lineage with zero trust in the publisher.
